descript.abstract: This dataset represents the country boundaries in the Southeast Asia region at a map scale of 1:3 million. This dataset is clipped from an updated version of the countries coverage in ESRI's ArcWorld Supplement data product.
descript.purpose: This dataset is used to create the SouthEastAsia.mxd map document.
descript.supplinf: This dataset is in Shapefile format, in Albers Conical Equal Area projection. Available attributes for the country polygons include country name.
